column5: So pretty
Beauty fish, great way to start the season!  Congrats.
Great fish Capt!!!  Congrats on that fine PB
Congrats on your PB and a awesome Walleye! WTG Captpeirre!

Awesome fish! I have a friend that owns a cottage resort on the Trent river..He says the gut bucket in the fish hut has been over half full every morning when he goes out. The walleye have been on fire this season so far..I'm on my way there tonight for the weekend!    The neat thing is he takes the gut bucket to a secret spot and feeds all the turtles.. There will be some fat turtles this year if the eyes keep biting the way they have been.. Anyway sorry to hijack your thread nice fish ya got there..Congrats on the PB!!!
Looks like that slot size is really helping out the kawarthas!

Fished a 10 ft deep weed flat with a perch crankbait at the cottage.  Thought I had a musky on the way it was pulling.  Very happy to see a 26 inch walleye.  Nice and fat.  Big breeder fish.  Had to go back in. Slot size is 30-50cm  Water temp 73.  Water clear
Nice  Congrats on you PB. Great fish
Congrats! Really nice walleye. Gotta be fun when you think a walleye is a musky.
Nice fish
Beauty Walleye for the Kawartha's!! Congrats!
Nice, and even better letting it swim away!
Congrats on the PB. Very healthy looking fish.
very nice, congrats
Nice catch...  That's a chunk walleye
congrats on your PB - nice looking fish,
congrats on your personal best eye !!! very nice fish...
nice eye!
Congrats on your PB.
She's a beaut!  Congrats!
Very nice fish!  73 degrees eh, should be a great opener this weekend.  What kind of perch crank was it?
Sweet catch!
Great job on the PB! Beauty fish!
Congrats!!!  A beauty walleye there....and kudos for releasing it to swim another day!
PB's are always nice.....walleye PB's are always just a little nicer     Beauty fish!!!
congratz on the PB! its a beauty
Congrats, beauty of an 'eye!!!!
Sweet wally !
Great job letting it go to produce some more monsters like that!
Congrats on the new PB eye great pic
Couldn't agree more. Congrats on a beauty walleye and double congrats on the release.
